des: "For serious garlic lovers! Start with 2 cloves garlic in this creamy, tangy dip and add more if you can handle it. Totally addictive. Serve with toasted Greek pita and raw vegetables."
ins: Combine the feta cheese, sour cream, yogurt and garlic in the container of a food processor or blender. Pulse briefly until garlic is minced. Spoon into a serving dish, and season with salt and pepper.
